com.facebook.buck.apple.toolchain

Interface UnresolvedAppleCxxPlatform

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FlavorConvertible
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProviderBackedUnresolvedAppleCxxPlatform, StaticUnresolvedAppleCxxPlatform

    public interface UnresolvedAppleCxxPlatform
extends FlavorConvertible
    Used by descriptions to properly handle AppleCxxPlatform. During parsing/configuration only information about parse-time deps is available. During action graph creation, this can be resolved to the final AppleCxxPlatform.
